
方法一：厂商/型号/ID
# dmidecode |grep -A4 'System Information' ##说明，不同的尝试可能-A 后面的行数不一样，建议先dmidecode下
System Information
	Manufacturer: HP
	Product Name: ProLiant DL380p Gen8
	Version: Not Specified
	Serial Number: 6CU4090CH4  
方法二
# grep 'DMI' /var/log/dmesg
[    0.000000] DMI: HP ProLiant BL460c Gen8, BIOS I31 03/01/2013


# dmidecode | grep "Product"
	Product Name: ProLiant DL380p Gen8
	String 2: Product ID: 653200-B21
